task.summary: Default task
Re-design and removed the parser hander for IParserHandler(parse) function
Remove the IParser interface and de-couple it from the crawler class for better design
Big re-design to almost all of the classes. Added integration-test profile
Implement result abstract class to hold the result for the match, and added tests for it + refactoring.
Added delimiter as property and also to the constructor for each Result classes
huge refactoring and re-design for the skeleton of the app. Added new test cases and de-couple the result class from useless props. Added exceptions for match class
Refactored and added tests.

Huge refactoring. Replaced the SL4J logging instead of logback. Added Utils class for matches with equal operation. Removed the interface of ICrawler concept, because the crawler is very basic class and its the same for every case.
Added readme
Fixed the resource reading class
Added data creator class which will crawl everything needed.Added mappings from the different domains
Added multiple encoding formats for supporting german language. Added test for the data crawler, refactored some things and implemented. Improved the skeleton design.
Added tests for data crawler class and continuing to implement it.

Added memorisation for crawling which will boost the performance of the class and continuing to implement it. Also added few new tests and changed the encoding to ISO for web crawler, because of the german letters. Made union of the ResultDB class and BundesLiga to more general one.
Removed the testng dependency and using the junit instead and also refactored.
Refactored and added benchmark for the collection data method
Refactoring and validate the all teams played in the bundesliga in period 2009-2014.
Refactoring and removed the depricated array assertion
Small improvements
